ns-de-risking-pressures-mount-says-foreign-affairs-expert?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国商界领袖敦促北京在私营部门的困境中“让常识占上风”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3252878/chinese-business-leader-urges-beijing-let-common-sense-prevail-amid-private-sector-struggles?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>当中国领导层打击私人补习行业时，俞敏洪的财富大幅缩水，现在他呼吁尊重市场经济规则。</description><pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 00:00:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3252878/chinese-business-leader-urges-beijing-let-common-sense-prevail-amid-private-sector-struggles?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>美国发展官员在攻击中国时宣称“慷慨”的援助植根于合作，“而不是债务陷阱”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3252906/jab-china-us-development-official-touts-big-hearted-aid-rooted-cooperation-not-debt-traps?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>私营部门对于帮助华盛顿推进全球南方的政策目标至关重要，以替代“永无止境的外国援助依赖”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 22:45:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3252906/jab-china-us-development-official-touts-big-hearted-aid-rooted-cooperation-not-debt-traps?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>美国大使表示，乌克兰战争周年纪念日临近，中国对俄罗斯的支持“非常令人不安”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3252896/chinas-support-russia-very-troubling-says-us-ambassador-anniversary-ukraine-war-looms?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>尼古拉斯·伯恩斯在北京的一次活动中表示，“中国在乌克兰主权和独立等事关生死存亡的问题上保持的沉默令人震耳欲聋”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 14:32:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3252896/chinas-support-russia-very-troubling-says-us-ambassador-anniversary-ukraine-war-looms?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国对拉美投资转向更小、更具战略性的项目</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3252865/chinas-latin-american-investments-downshift-smaller-more-strategic-projects?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>像“一带一路”倡议这样的高风险、高成本的大型基础设施项目受欢迎程度下降，现在出现在回报更快、运营成本更低的领域。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 14:00:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3252865/chinas-latin-american-investments-downshift-smaller-more-strategic-projects?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国科技巨头联想在全球最大的个人电脑制造商公布自 2022 年底以来首次季度收入增长后，加倍押注人工智能</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3252871/chinese-tech-giant-lenovo-doubles-down-ai-after-worlds-largest-pc-maker-posts-first-quarterly?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>联想对人工智能的高度关注反映了个人电脑行业对支持该技术的机器的需求预计变化的反应。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 13:30:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3252871/chinese-tech-giant-lenovo-doubles-down-ai-after-worlds-largest-pc-maker-posts-first-quarterly?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国和沙特阿拉伯希望加强航空客运联系</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3252882/china-and-saudi-arabia-looking-boost-air-passenger-links?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>该倡议是继一系列经济和安全倡议之后，两国为建立更紧密联系而做出的最新努力。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 13:10:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3252882/china-and-saudi-arabia-looking-boost-air-passenger-links?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>为什么特朗普和美国大选可能会增加中国在寻求更加“理性”的欧洲信任时的机会</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3252883/why-trump-us-elections-may-buoy-chinas-chances-it-seeks-gain-trust-more-rational-europe?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>王毅外长结束三国之行回国后表示，欧洲对中国的理性认识不断增强。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 13:02:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3252883/why-trump-us-elections-may-buoy-chinas-chances-it-seeks-gain-trust-more-rational-europe?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国提振经济的基础设施计划会不会给工程带来矛盾？</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3252875/could-chinas-economy-boosting-infrastructure-plans-throw-contradictory-monkey-wrench-works?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>努力减少地方政府债务，同时通过投资提振中国地方经济被认为是一种相互矛盾的做法，而工程机械业务的下降也不是好兆头。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 12:30:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3252875/could-chinas-economy-boosting-infrastructure-plans-throw-contradictory-monkey-wrench-works?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>经济学家表示，中国迫切需要发放“最有效”的现金券来刺激消费不足</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3252843/china-urgently-needs-issue-most-effective-cash-coupons-boost-insufficient-consumption-economist-says?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>著名经济学家滕泰表示，现金券是鼓励消费的“最有效方式”，北京已经响应了发放现金券和消费券以帮助经济复苏的呼声。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 12:30:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3252843/china-urgently-needs-issue-most-effective-cash-coupons-boost-insufficient-consumption-economist-says?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>随着北京重启大熊猫外交，中国“友好使者”将重返美国动物园</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3252870/chinas-envoys-friendship-return-us-zoo-beijing-restarts-panda-diplomacy?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>与圣地亚哥动物园的合作协议标志着中国改善与西方关系的最新努力。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 12:01:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3252870/chinas-envoys-friendship-return-us-zoo-beijing-restarts-panda-diplomacy?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>两岸紧张局势加剧之际，美国国会代表团开始访台</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3252847/us-congressional-delegation-starts-taiwan-visit-amid-heightened-cross-strait-tensions?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>主要对华鹰派迈克·加拉格尔 (Mike Gallagher) 表示，美国对台湾的支持“坚如磐石”，无论 11 月选举结果如何，这种支持都将持续下去</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 11:00:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3252847/us-congressional-delegation-starts